Ambalavao; Réserve naturelle n|1 5; Andringitra. Valley of R. Zomandao, 5 km. S. of Antanifotsy. Metamorphic formation; rainfall c. 1600 mm p.a. Forest of western formation; Brachylaena, Tambourissa, Weinmannia forest with many Araliaceae & Cyathea at streamsides. Undergrowth thick; mainly Acanthaceae. Surrounded by secondary grassland & Philippia brush.
